Commentary Text: Stoinis to Miller, out Caught by Hooda!! GT finish with 135 as Stoinis gets his 100th T20 wicket. Miller c Hooda b Stoinis 6(12)

Commentary Text: Mishra to Abhinav Manohar, out Caught by Naveen-ul-Haq!! Brilliant take from Naveen-ul-Haq and that is a fielder's wicket for sure! Credit to Mishra too as he outsmarted the batter. Bowls a loopy ball well outside off, Abhinav Manohar reaches out to it and tries to hit an expansive shot down the ground but ends up slicing it over extra cover. Commentary Text: Noor Ahmad to Pooran, out Caught by Hardik Pandya!! Another one bites the dust! A tossed up delivery on off, touch fuller, Pooran goes for a slogsweep as a thick top edge is induced. Hardik Pandya settles underneath the skier, and completes a safe reverse cup before his back hits the floor. So many times we have seen this in the IPL.
